  <h2>Detailed JQL Explanation</h2>
  <h3>Fields (sample list)</h3>
  <p>Used to filter/search for issues:</p>
  <p>Assignee, Affected version, Attachments, Comment, Component, Created, Description, Due, Filter, Fix version, Issue key, Labels, Priority, Project, Reporter, Sprint, Status, Summary, Time spent, Watcher</p>

  <h3>Operators</h3>
  <p>=, >, >=, ~, in, is, was, changed, !=, <, <=, !~, not in, is not</p>

  <h3>Functions</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Time</strong>: startOfDay(), endOfMonth(), now()</li>
    <li><strong>People</strong>: currentUser(), membersOf()</li>
    <li><strong>Issue</strong>: issueHistory(), openSprints(), watchedIssues()</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Reserved Characters</h3>
  <p>" ", +, ., ,, ;, ?, `, *, /, %, ^, $, #, @, [, ]</p>

  <h3>Reserved Words</h3>
  <p>a, and, as, at, be, but, by, for, if, in, into, is, it, no, not, of, on, or, such, the, their, this, to, was, will, with</p>

  <h3>Term Modifiers</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Wildcard <code>?</code>: Single character (e.g. <code>te?t</code>)</li>
    <li>Wildcard <code>*</code>: Multiple characters (e.g. <code>win*</code>)</li>
    <li>Proximity: <code>"Atlassian jira"~10</code></li>
    <li>Fuzzy: <code>roam~</code></li>
    <li>Boost: <code>atlassian^4 jira</code></li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Learn more:</strong> <a href="https://docs.atlassian.com/advanced-searching" target="_blank">Atlassian Advanced Searching Docs</a></p>

